data.description: Nestled within the prestigious Lake Forest Subdivision, 3 Maple Tree Lane offers a captivating blend of modern elegance and serene lakeside living. This meticulously crafted residence presents an unparalleled opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of luxury, tranquility, and convenience. Enjoy access to a range of amenities, including community pool, lake, tennis courts, trails, playground, gym and a clubhouse. The property features generously sized bedrooms, open floor plan, gas fireplace, granite countertops, bonus room which could be a 4th bedroom, covered patio, and fenced yard. Convenient to airport, Arsenal Gate 7, Stadium and shops!
